OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1776258665
OL,3,CFraudster who sold fake Oasis tickets
OL,4,Cto pay off debts sentenced
OL,6,FA fraudster who sold fake Oasis
OL,7,Fconcert tickets to pay off her debts
OL,8,Fhas been handed a community order and
OL,9,Ftold to pay a fine of #40 - and
OL,10,Fcompensation of #776.98 to five of her
OL,11,Fvictims.
OL,13,FRosie Slater, 33, used her connections
OL,14,Fwith "wealthy, rich and famous people"
OL,15,Fto dupe 11 people who lost an
OL,16,Festimated total of #4,000,
OL,17,FStaffordshire Police said.
OL,26,@vD@FOUvD@fO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/10
