OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1776258665
OL,3,CFraudster who sold fake Oasis tickets
OL,4,Cto pay off debts sentenced
OL,6,FSlater, who admitted 11 counts of
OL,7,Ffraud by false representation at a
OL,8,Fhearing in December, sat in front of
OL,9,Fthe glass dock at North Staffordshire
OL,10,FJustice Centre on Monday, wearing a
OL,11,Fblack outfit with a black blazer over
OL,12,Fthe top.
OL,14,FProsecutor Kyle Padley said Slater,
OL,15,Fformerly of Betley in Newcastle-under-
OL,16,FLyme, Staffordshire, told her victims
OL,17,Fshe had access to Oasis tickets,
OL,18,Fincluding for the VIP box at Wembley
OL,19,FStadium.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1776258665
OL,3,CFraudster who sold fake Oasis tickets
OL,4,Cto pay off debts sentenced
OL,6,FOne man, who bought 15 tickets from
OL,7,Fher, set up two WhatsApp groups and
OL,8,Finvited friends he thought might want
OL,9,Fto buy some, the court heard.
OL,11,FIn those groups, Slater offered a
OL,12,Fprice of #130 per ticket, and some
OL,13,Fpeople sent her the money directly and
OL,14,Fbooked non-refundable hotel rooms for
OL,15,Fthe concert dates.
OL,17,FMr Padley told the court: "It later
OL,18,Fcame out the defendant was lying."
OL,26,@yD@[OUzD@bO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1776258665
OL,3,CFraudster who sold fake Oasis tickets
OL,4,Cto pay off debts sentenced
OL,6,FHe said she was then interviewed by
OL,7,Fpolice, adding: "She said she started
OL,8,Fwith good intent then it escalated out
OL,9,Fof her control."
OL,11,FThe defendant was handed a 12-month
OL,12,Fcommunity order and must pay a #40
OL,13,Ffine and compensation of #776.98 to
OL,14,Ffive of her victims.
OL,16,FSome of her victims have already been
OL,17,Fable to get refunds, the court heard.
OL,26,@oD@QOUqD@PO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1776258665
OL,3,CFraudster who sold fake Oasis tickets
OL,4,Cto pay off debts sentenced
OL,6,FSlater was also told to pay a #114
OL,7,Fvictim surcharge and costs of #85, and
OL,8,Fwill complete 30 rehabilitation
OL,9,Factivity requirement days as part of
OL,10,Fher sentence.
OL,12,FSimon Leech, defending Slater, told
OL,13,Fthe court "she did not spend this
OL,14,Fmoney extravagantly" and that she used
OL,15,Fit to pay off household debts
OL,16,Fincluding council tax payments.
OL,26,@uD@KOUvD@TO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1776258665
OL,3,CFraudster who sold fake Oasis tickets
OL,4,Cto pay off debts sentenced
OL,6,FDetective Constable David Stubbs, of
OL,7,FStaffordshire Police, told LBC: "She
OL,8,Fdoes have connections with some of our
OL,9,Fwealthy, rich and famous people and
OL,10,Fhas been fortunate enough to
OL,11,Fpreviously attend concerts, and due to
OL,12,Fthis she was able to convince her
OL,13,Fvictims that she had credible access
OL,14,Fto both the tickets and the VIP box at
OL,15,FWembley Stadium.
OL,17,F"No evidence has been found of any
OL,18,Fcoercion. She has acted, we believe,
OL,19,Fpurely out of greed, exploiting her
OL,20,Fconnections for personal gain.
OL,26,@oD@aOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1776258665
OL,3,CFraudster who sold fake Oasis tickets
OL,4,Cto pay off debts sentenced
OL,6,F"This has left the victims obviously
OL,7,Fvery upset. It's caused a lot of anger
OL,8,Fand hurt, really, particularly as she
OL,9,Fused some of the victims to attract
OL,10,Fmore victims."
OL,12,FA Competition and Markets Authority
OL,13,F(CMA) investigation was launched into
OL,14,Fthe way Ticketmaster sold Oasis
OL,15,Ftickets in 2024.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@NO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1776258665
OL,3,CFraudster who sold fake Oasis tickets
OL,4,Cto pay off debts sentenced
OL,6,FThe probe found Ticketmaster did not
OL,7,Ftell fans waiting in lengthy queues
OL,8,Fthat standing tickets were being sold
OL,9,Fat two different prices, and that
OL,10,Fprices would jump as soon as the cheap
OL,11,Ftickets sold out.
OL,13,FTicketmaster sold some "platinum"
OL,14,Ftickets at almost two and a half times
OL,15,Fthe price of standard tickets, without
OL,16,Fsufficient explanation that these
OL,17,Foffered no additional benefits in the
OL,18,Fsame areas of the venue, the CMA said.
OL,26,@uD@XOUuD@aO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1776258665
OL,3,CFraudster who sold fake Oasis tickets
OL,4,Cto pay off debts sentenced
OL,6,FIn response, the CMA said Ticketmaster
OL,7,Fmust now tell fans 24 hours in advance
OL,8,Fif a tiered pricing system is being
OL,9,Fused ` as it was for Oasis standing
OL,10,Ftickets.
OL,12,FTickets for the band's reunion tour,
OL,13,Fwhich were their first gigs in 16
OL,14,Fyears, were also listed on secondary
OL,15,Fticket resale websites for thousands
OL,16,Fof pounds.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
